transcripts.text: So I got a new one of these things, because the old one is all... rusty and shitty and it's falling apart.  But this one... This is the first time I'm using it, and I don't know if the camera can see it, but the fucking paint is coming off.  The fuck is that shit?  Look, it's like bubbling.  The fuck?  Why even put the paint on there?  Because it's gonna fucking burn off the first time you use it.  What kind of shit is that?
